@startuml
title Client Result Error Envelope (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #D6EAF8
component "createClient(...)" as Client #D5F5E3
component "Table/RPC/Query Builder" as Builder #FCF3CF
component "Athena Gateway Client" as Gateway #FADBD8
component "AthenaResult<T>\n{ data, error: string | null,\n  errorDetails?, status }" as Result #E8DAEF
component "normalizeAthenaError(result, context?)" as Normalize #FDEBD0

Consumer --> Client : configure URL/key
Client --> Builder : from()/rpc()/query()
Builder --> Gateway : execute HTTP call
Gateway --> Result : error string + gateway metadata
Consumer --> Normalize : optional follow-up call
Normalize --> Consumer : kind/table/operation metadata

note right of Result
Useful fields were split:
- error string on the result
- hint/request info in errorDetails
- normalized classification via helper
end note
@enduml
